Class HolonomicDrivetrain

  • java.lang.Object
    • ftc.team6460.javadeck.api.motion.impl.HolonomicDrivetrain

    VelocityDrivetrain

    public class HolonomicDrivetrain
extends java.lang.Object
implements VelocityDrivetrain
    The motor polarity is assumed such that positive power causes that motor, as seen from outside robot, to spin clockwise.
